{"tid":1951362,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[繼續餓死藍屍]2月份零售銷售數據會是有紀錄以來的最大跌幅","createTime":"2020-03-31T02:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T03:01:58.000Z","uid":326897,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"992a2d458a2f7e054aeb05c3380cf365110f403a","tid":1951362,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:37:30.000Z","msg":"特首：零售數據歷來最大跌幅 第二輪抗疫基金涉數百億<br />\n2020-03-31 HKT 10:02<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517897-20200331.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517897-20200331.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=bbb2f17b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517897-20200331.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0dd6dd3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517897-20200331.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n特首：零售數據歷來最大跌幅 第二輪抗疫基金涉數百億<br />\n新型肺炎疫情持續，行政長官林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，本港面對的打擊是史無前例，政府下午公布的2月份零售銷售數據會是有紀錄以來的最大跌幅，飲食及零售業面對困難，政府希望可以盡快回應，讓員工不會被裁減。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，在公布一系列嚴厲措施時已承諾，特區政府會啟動第二輪防疫抗疫基金，再次動用數以百億元，為水深火熱行業及員工提供適切協助，亦有與持分者會面。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出，已與地產建設商會見面，希望他們可以減租，呼籲業主共渡時艱。她又說，已指示政府部門檢視旗下出租商舖，檢視有無進一步減租空間。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繼續加油，餓死廢老藍屍，<br />\n支持黃色經濟圈，wiki，光時日日買，<br />\n美心，小米等仆街</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9224363563c6861e1d89826d2491fe63dd367852","tid":1951362,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:37:48.000Z","msg":"開始日日都有還押幾個月手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1951351\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1951351</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ddf5ad19ac69d01c577bc9d14f3dcbf64156389","tid":1951362,"uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"衰過沙士 衰過沙士<br />\n呢鑊真係開口中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd941975e704eadf1abf175c78dac154f04ab7dd","tid":1951362,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:41:53.000Z","msg":"最慘都係佔中果班仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a1a17b319166846ea22b7cc732d7432ca992e9","tid":1951362,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"D紅底藍底大集團好捱得 冇咁易死<br />\nD黃小店仲大獲"},{"pid":"31fcf970b2d0032840408f3f1bed0adcae173d0b","tid":1951362,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"成日話生意差，但啲野就唔減價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2bf16fd7be4ff1c0161ab5f51c653d3317f5be7","tid":1951362,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ddf5ad19ac69d01c577bc9d14f3dcbf64156389","tid":1951362,"uid":10338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:38:17.000Z","msg":"衰過沙士 衰過沙士<br />\n呢鑊真係開口中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:58:04.000Z","msg":"人禍咎由自取，<br />\n人人俾機會提醒，但自以為是，<br />\n一步一步咁推香港去地獄，<br />\n信佢嗰班藍屍等死啦"},{"pid":"d3227fbb3bc94de93940d63d7cffe70e7fc49bb0","tid":1951362,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9a1a17b319166846ea22b7cc732d7432ca992e9","tid":1951362,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T02:43:31.000Z","msg":"D紅底藍底大集團好捱得 冇咁易死<br />\nD黃小店仲大獲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T03:01:58.000Z","msg":"骨牌效應，睇下捱得幾耐，<br />\n好多底學歷藍屍廢老冇工開，<br />\n地盤藍屍摺鳩晒，<br />\n<br />\n一齊攬炒，<br />\n等班撐政府廢柴反淋病枱，<br />\n到時全香港connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}